Date: Sat, 9 Mar 2024 01:13:08 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 27/38] ARM: dts: stm32: Add alternate pinmux for MP13 PWM5
 pins

Add another mux option for PWM5 pins, this is used on
DH electronics STM32MP13xx DHCOR DHSBC board.

Upstream-Status: Submitted [https://patchwork.ozlabs.org/project/uboot/patch/20240421231849.194648-8-marex@denx.de/]
Signed-off-by: Marek Vasut <marex@denx.de>
---
Cc: Patrice Chotard <patrice.chotard@foss.st.com>
Cc: Patrick Delaunay <patrick.delaunay@foss.st.com>
Cc: u-boot@dh-electronics.com
Cc: uboot-stm32@st-md-mailman.stormreply.com
---
 arch/arm/dts/stm32mp13-pinctrl.dtsi | 15 +++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 15 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/dts/stm32mp13-pinctrl.dtsi b/arch/arm/dts/stm32mp13-pinctrl.dtsi
index b58bf6c0024..d19408f19f9 100644
--- a/arch/arm/dts/stm32mp13-pinctrl.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm/dts/stm32mp13-pinctrl.dtsi
@@ -245,6 +245,21 @@
 		};
 	};
 
+	pwm5_pins_a: pwm5-0 {
+		pins {
+			pinmux = <STM32_PINMUX('H', 12, AF2)>; /* TIM5_CH3 */
+			bias-pull-down;
+			drive-push-pull;
+			slew-rate = <0>;
+		};
+	};
+
+	pwm5_sleep_pins_a: pwm5-sleep-0 {
+		pins {
+			pinmux = <STM32_PINMUX('H', 12, ANALOG)>; /* TIM5_CH3 */
+		};
+	};
+
 	pwm8_pins_a: pwm8-0 {
 		pins {
 			pinmux = <STM32_PINMUX('E', 5, AF3)>; /* TIM8_CH3 */
-- 
